{
  "2306620": {
    "name": "雨中冒险 2: 风暴探寻者",
    "steam_appid": 2306620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/72aa950c668ea5892fea8353c0eb3bbb.avif?t=1750149470\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>虚假救世主</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让琼泥V受到应有的惩罚，并开辟一条通往巨像的道路来面对远古威胁！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个灵魂，生来毫无目的，身负枷锁，被人遗忘。她的监狱，既是避难所，也是牢笼。她的命运：因她完美的设计，注定毁灭。几千年过去了。她越来越绝望，她从孤独的深处，把另一位带进了她失落的世界。现在，虚假子嗣行走在琼泥V上，被他祖先的背叛和国王盲目野心的腐败所束缚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/3e1b5cb0c7c3a62d44ba8c78c4cbffdf.poster.avif?t=1750149470\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/3e1b5cb0c7c3a62d44ba8c78c4cbffdf.webm?t=1750149470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/3e1b5cb0c7c3a62d44ba8c78c4cbffdf.mp4?t=1750149470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>征服巨像之路</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备深入探险琼泥V的失落区域吧！随着新关卡的推进，远古利莫里亚神殿和倾泻而下的瀑布将映入你的眼帘。你可以探索隐藏的洞穴，并在蠕虫巢穴中体会硫磺的独特气味。也可以在重塑祭坛内抵御数十名利莫里亚人，还可以进入树民聚落那郁郁葱葱的绿色树冠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但真正的威胁就悬在头顶……踏上巨像之路，在与虚假子嗣的较量中提升巨像等级。打败他，释放他灵魂的真正力量！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/f49b1fdff6b405b40413682a72133739.poster.avif?t=1750149470\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/f49b1fdff6b405b40413682a72133739.webm?t=1750149470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/f49b1fdff6b405b40413682a72133739.mp4?t=1750149470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>幸存者 1：利用探寻者掌握灵魂精魄</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在出神入化的灵魂操控能力加持下，探寻者可以对附近的怪物造成巨大伤害，同时释放强大的治疗能力来为队友提供支援。这种战斗与治疗的独特组合让探寻者成为了幸存者。学会在这些角色之间无缝转换的玩家将获得最神通广大的幸存者之一，为逃生舱增光添彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦达到足够平静的状态，你甚至可以让倒下的盟友复活！探寻者的存在可以扭转任何战斗的局势，既可带来毁灭，也可带来救赎。拥抱双面能力，带领你的团队走向胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >风暴探寻者的拥有者将立即解锁探寻者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/1af7c0dbc74425e95274b367425a2995.poster.avif?t=1750149470\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/1af7c0dbc74425e95274b367425a2995.webm?t=1750149470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/1af7c0dbc74425e95274b367425a2995.mp4?t=1750149470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>幸存者 2：与大厨一起尽情烹饪吧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大厨回来了！但这不是你爷爷的大厨机器人。多年的战斗磨炼了他的灵魂，完善了他的烹饪技能。昔日大厨的长腿换成了巨大的滚轮——它非常适合压出漂亮、整齐的馅饼皮，或者碾过今早不幸醒来的无助利莫里亚人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多年来，大厨经历了各种烹饪方面的不幸，因此他已经能够熟练地使用他那把值得信赖的切肉刀。他能向远处的敌人投掷切肉刀，并将其召回，让敌人感受双倍的切割痛苦。掌握切肉刀的艺术，在血肉横飞中取得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >烹饪出真正美味佳肴的玩家将解锁大厨！所以，准备好在敌群中杀出一条血路，将战斗技能与烹饪技巧相结合，并以最时髦的方式伸张正义吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/682013d6196d02c007e8f162c31ad218.poster.avif?t=1750149470\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/682013d6196d02c007e8f162c31ad218.webm?t=1750149470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/682013d6196d02c007e8f162c31ad218.mp4?t=1750149470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>幸存者 3：与虚假子嗣一起奋力获得救赎</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将虚假子嗣从枷锁中解放出来，发挥他巨大的力量！这个构造体被雕刻成神的形象，由空洞之王的腐化和黄金巨人的心脏锻造而成，这甚至让他强大到能够抗衡神本尊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虚假子嗣擅长成为无法移动的物体。他巨大的体型、令人难以置信的生命值以及无与伦比的再生能力使他成为拥有超凡韧性的幸存者。在近距离遭遇战中，敌人将在他巨大棍棒的碾压下屈服。然而，在棍棒范围之外，战斗变得更加具有挑战性。策略性地利用视线吸引敌人，或用精心投掷的月之刺将他们击倒。学会快速接近敌人，你就能从这个威风的傀儡身上榨取最大的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/2087ac7da19a10c0aaef41f896cf7703.poster.avif?t=1750149470\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/2087ac7da19a10c0aaef41f896cf7703.webm?t=1750149470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306620/extras/2087ac7da19a10c0aaef41f896cf7703.mp4?t=1750149470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只需一名玩家拥有“风暴探寻者”即可为整个大厅启用扩展包。没有“风暴探寻者”的玩家将无法选择新幸存者或永久解锁新物品、日志或其他内容。</p>",
